OL,3,CCouncil wants crackdown on antisocial
OL,4,Cbehaviour including fines for swearing
OL,6,FA council in Kent is looking to
OL,7,Fcrackdown on antisocial behaviour by
OL,8,Fseeking permission for an order which
OL,9,Fcould land people with a fine for
OL,10,Fswearing.
OL,12,FThanet District Council is asking for
OL,13,Fapproval for a Public Spaces
OL,14,FProtection Order to address issues of
OL,15,Fantisocial behaviour in Ramsgate,
OL,16,FBroadstairs and Margate.
