OL,3,CCouncil wants crackdown on antisocial
OL,4,Cbehaviour including fines for swearing
OL,6,FIt's after the area recently faced
OL,7,Fissues including what police have
OL,8,Fdescribed as 'underage street drinking
OL,9,Fand aggressive behaviour towards staff
OL,10,Fat shops and restaurants'.
OL,12,FOrders proposed by the council include
OL,13,Fusing foul or abusive language within
OL,14,Fthe hearing or sight of another
OL,15,Fperson, urinating, defecating or
OL,16,Fspitting in a public place and taking
OL,17,Fpsychoactive substances such as
OL,18,Fnitrous oxide.
