OL,3,CCouncil wants crackdown on antisocial
OL,4,Cbehaviour including fines for swearing
OL,6,FCouncil documents state the
OL,7,Frestriction is not intended to
OL,8,Fpenalise 'casual or non-directed
OL,9,Fswearing' and that in order to be
OL,10,Fenforceable, the behaviour must be
OL,11,Fboth 'foul or abusive in nature and
OL,12,Flikely to cause harassment, alarm or
OL,13,Fdistress to a reasonable person'.
