OL,3,CCouncil wants crackdown on antisocial
OL,4,Cbehaviour including fines for swearing
OL,6,FIn response to the application for an
OL,7,Forder, Chief Inspector Ian Swallow
OL,8,Fsaid in a letter: "We believe that the
OL,9,Fimplementation of the PSPO is a
OL,10,Fnecessary measure to reduce crime,
OL,11,Fdisorder and ASB on the Thanet
OL,12,FDistrict, and to provide Officers and
OL,13,Fstaff suitable powers to deal with
OL,14,Fsuch behaviour.
OL,16,F"Failure to implement the PSPO would,
OL,17,Fin our opinion, be detrimental to
OL,18,FCommunity Safety in the district."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/5
