OL,3,CCouncil wants crackdown on antisocial
OL,4,Cbehaviour including fines for swearing
OL,6,FIf approved, enforcement officers
OL,7,Fwould have the authority to issue
OL,8,Ffines of #100 which would need to be
OL,9,Fpaid within 28 days, but is reduced to
OL,10,F#60 if paid within 14 days.
OL,12,FThe PSPO would be in place for a
OL,13,Fperiod of three years.
OL,15,FThe council did seek to implement a
OL,16,Fpublic order last summer, however this
OL,17,Fwas halted after a threat of a legal
OL,18,Fchallenge.
OL,20,FThe order is due to be discussed at a
OL,21,Fcabinet meeting next Thursday.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/5
